rld you are moving in is beautiful. The soundtrack might be the best I have ever heard while playing a game. The creative effort of the developers can be seen and is astounding.But the core mechanics of the game are either not fun or stupid. Fights never feel smooth and losing abilities is worsening the entire system even more.All in all the game is a sold 10/10 in presentation of its content while being a 3/10 in everything else.That is just my two cents on the whole thing, I guess you can totally check it out for yourself to get amazed by the gorgeous way Transistor is abled to show its story to the player. But it totally is not worth the 20 bucks."
