ls alot about the human nature and it's instinct to be selfish. Deeper thoughts can be put into the storyline to reveal much much more about the settings and the story.)Music: 10/10 (Beautiful. Fits into the settings perfectly. Go and listen for yourself :).)Overall score: 9~/10Would recommend?: Definitely"
