ry crucial to carefully plan how much energy you want to spend on moving and attacking during the planning phase. Overall the gameplay makes a nice blend between action- and strategy-games and fits perfectly into this virtual sci-fi world 10/10."");System.out.println(opinion+"": ""+""For its 18,99€ pricetag (27.05.2014) it's definetly worth buying in my opinion, even with a quite short playtime of 6 hours for the 1st playthrough. But it is important to know that depending on how many enemies you fight and your difficulty settings you may not even have unlocked all abilities (functions) by the end of the game. Which is not really a problem because you can just start all over and level up until lvl 31 while unlocking additional slots for your functions and gaining more points to spend on your functions. So I'm definetly going to play this game a 2nd time ;).Very enjoyable game from the very beginning until the end. (^.^)b"");}}"
