 doge anything. Recharging takes 3 or 5 seconds, enough time to take half of my hp away.Single skills without the use of the space skill, takes too long to execute, takes too long to reload, and too weak to be worth doing.I'm now at the part where you can do the speed test. And so far the controls is just too awful for me to continue. But, I will be fair. I will try a few more levels and hope that the controls will improve.I will edit this again tomorrow for my final verdict.*EDIT*Ok I have given all I can for this game. I'm sorry but the controls and combat style is really not for me. Everything is too slow. I'm too stressed out to continue playing. And to all who says ""If you like Bastion you should play this game"", you should be ashamed."
